272
00:19:11.498 --> 00:19:12.791
She's flirting.

273
00:19:13.041 --> 00:19:16.378
But seriously.
this is tremendously exciting.

274
00:19:16.586 --> 00:19:19.673
The knowledge. the new ideas:
it'll change everything.

275
00:19:20.090 --> 00:19:22.008
And we must be open to it.

276
00:19:22.175 --> 00:19:24.761
Maybe they can tell us about our universe.

277
00:19:24.844 --> 00:19:26.179
How it started.

278
00:19:26.346 --> 00:19:27.847
Where it's going.

279
00:19:28.014 --> 00:19:30.267
Perhaps even its purpose.

280
00:19:31.017 --> 00:19:32.602
It's tremendously exciting.

281
00:19:32.686 --> 00:19:35.355
It's the most important event since...

282
00:19:35.689 --> 00:19:37.941
...Jesus walked in Galilee--

283
00:19:38.608 --> 00:19:39.776
Christ.

284
00:19:39.943 --> 00:19:41.611
What's wrong?

285
00:19:41.778 --> 00:19:43.029
Go to Camera Two!

286
