I can't. It's busted.

287
00:19:44.614 --> 00:19:46.449
Go to One! Go to Four!

288
00:19:53.039 --> 00:19:54.457
He copped a feel.

289
00:19:57.044 --> 00:19:58.212
Now what?

290
00:20:11.642 --> 00:20:12.852
What's that?

291
00:20:13.060 --> 00:20:14.645
So that's a Martian.

292
00:20:17.899 --> 00:20:19.317
That's a Martian?

293
