I hope so.

373
00:25:14.367 --> 00:25:15.993
Army trains them good.

374
00:25:21.415 --> 00:25:23.000
He's gone for a while.

375
00:25:23.834 --> 00:25:26.337
Why can't you be more like your brother?

376
00:25:26.504 --> 00:25:30.758
We got lucky with Billy-Glenn.
You can't expect the same luck twice.

377
00:25:31.342 --> 00:25:34.512
Richie. want to make yourself useful
for a change?

378
00:25:34.679 --> 00:25:35.763
Sure. Dad.

379
00:25:35.846 --> 00:25:37.848
Take Grandma back to the home.

380
00:25:51.862 --> 00:25:55.324
I bet you never thought you'd live
to see the Martians come.

381
00:25:55.784 --> 00:25:57.703
It's pretty far out.

382
