384
00:26:08.046 --> 00:26:10.799
Come on. kid. I'm not that old!

385
00:26:14.303 --> 00:26:15.554
Are you okay?

386
00:26:17.222 --> 00:26:18.807
I want to see Slim.

387
00:26:18.974 --> 00:26:20.309
I want to see...

388
00:26:20.475 --> 00:26:21.727
...Slim...

389
00:26:21.894 --> 00:26:23.228
...and Muffy...

390
00:26:23.645 --> 00:26:24.980
...and Richie.

391
00:26:27.983 --> 00:26:29.526
Grandma. I'm Richie.

392
00:26:31.069 --> 00:26:32.988
I know. Thomas.

393
00:26:33.322 --> 00:26:35.908
Richie was always the best one.

394
00:26:39.870 --> 00:26:43.165
Right now the president
is talking to other world leaders.

395
00:26:43.248 --> 00:26:46.835
