That's my Muffy.

417
00:28:24.268 --> 00:28:27.104
Didn't you ever have
a pussycat of your own?

418
00:28:27.271 --> 00:28:28.522
Sure. Grandma.

419
00:28:28.772 --> 00:28:30.524
Music!

420
00:28:35.779 --> 00:28:37.031
There you go.

421
00:28:41.702 --> 00:28:43.454
You going to be okay?

422
00:28:44.371 --> 00:28:48.375
lf you need anything.
any doughnuts or anything. call me.

423
00:29:14.611 --> 00:29:15.946
How do?

