428
00:29:30.543 --> 00:29:34.631
I made a ton of money
on your last fight in '73.

429
00:29:34.798 --> 00:29:36.424
The Quaker in Jamaica.

430
00:29:37.217 --> 00:29:38.802
I'm glad somebody did.

431
00:29:38.969 --> 00:29:41.054
Yeah. I know. I know.

432
00:29:41.221 --> 00:29:42.764
It's rough on jocks.

433
