I'm trying to get back with my wife.

446
00:30:20.678 --> 00:30:23.097
We had problems with this kind of shit.

447
00:30:23.931 --> 00:30:25.683
But I've changed. man.

448
00:30:25.933 --> 00:30:27.018
I found Allah...

449
00:30:27.101 --> 00:30:29.604
