450
00:30:30.688 --> 00:30:33.774
I faced that demon
and I don't want him coming again.

451
00:30:36.027 --> 00:30:38.029
You gave up pork!

452
00:30:45.244 --> 00:30:47.163
They're sending coordinates.

453
00:30:53.127 --> 00:30:54.211
