454
00:30:54.296 --> 00:30:56.506
Pahrump. It's in the Nevada desert.

455
00:30:56.590 --> 00:30:59.760
I can have my troops there at 0800 hours.
sir.

456
00:30:59.968 --> 00:31:03.639
We must not send these people
