475
00:32:24.220 --> 00:32:25.889
Isn't that great?

476
00:32:26.055 --> 00:32:28.933
Oh. it's a hell of an honor.

477
00:32:29.392 --> 00:32:33.938
Didn't I always tell you if I stayed
in place and never spoke up...

478
00:32:34.105 --> 00:32:36.566
...good things were bound to happen?

479
00:33:43.634 --> 00:33:47.179
I want the Martians to be treated
like foreign dignitaries.

480
00:33:47.346 --> 00:33:49.974
I want your men alert and majestic...

481
00:33:50.140 --> 00:33:52.643
...with a snap in their step.

482
00:33:53.853 --> 00:33:56.523
