The world is watching.

483
00:33:56.606 --> 00:33:57.691
Yes. sir.

484
00:34:02.862 --> 00:34:05.240
Are you positive this thing will work?

485
00:34:06.324 --> 00:34:08.034
Positively positive.

486
00:34:08.201 --> 00:34:09.786
We don't want any slip-ups.

487
00:34:09.869 --> 00:34:11.997
No. no. no. no. Not at all.

488
00:34:33.518 --> 00:34:36.313
Poppy. All these people.

489
00:34:37.147 --> 00:34:39.524
All of them here to see you.

490
00:34:42.319 --> 00:34:44.154
There's Jason. Poppy!

491
00:34:57.001 --> 00:34:58.502
Okay. let's go.

492
00:35:00.713 --> 00:35:04.091
The teeming masses have gathered
from who knows how many states...

493
00:35:04.175 --> 00:35:06.010
