494
00:35:06.218 --> 00:35:07.595
Why have they come?

495
00:35:07.678 --> 00:35:10.056
Curiosity? Or is it something more?

496
00:35:10.389 --> 00:35:13.100
Or simply to say. 'I was there'?

497
00:35:13.559 --> 00:35:14.936
'I was there...

498
00:35:15.102 --> 00:35:16.687
'...when first man...

499
00:35:16.771 --> 00:35:18.272
